PRIVACY POLICY FOR CURRENCYFLOW
Last Updated: November 2025
INFORMATION WE COLLECT
- Device Information: Device model, iOS version, app usage statistics
- Usage Analytics: App interaction patterns (through Apple analytics)
- Location Data: None collected (no location services needed)
- Personal Information: None required (no user accounts or sign-ups)
- Exchange Rate Data: Fetched from public API sources only
HOW WE USE INFORMATION
- Improve app performance and reliability
- Analyze usage to enhance user experience
- Comply with legal obligations
- Provide accurate currency conversion services
DATA STORAGE & SECURITY
- Conversion history stored locally on your device only
- Favorite currencies stored locally on your device only
- No personal data transmitted to our servers
- HTTPS/TLS encryption for all API communications
- No user accounts = no data on cloud servers
THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
- Currency Exchange API (for real-time rates)
- Apple Analytics (standard iOS metrics)
- No data sharing with third parties
USER RIGHTS
- You can delete app data by uninstalling the app
- You have the right to contact us with privacy concerns
- You can request information about data collection
CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
CurrencyFlow does not target children under 13.
We do not knowingly collect data from children.
Parental permission recommended for children using the app.
CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update this policy. Continued use indicates acceptance of updates.
